title: ACC Championship Preview:  Florida State vs. Georgia Tech
description:
The #4 Florida State Seminoles look to defend their ACC title this Saturday night in Charlotte as they face Coastal Division champion Georgia Tech.  Join Ryan Pensy, Brandon Mellor and Mike Sage for the best preview you will find online.

They also discuss the following:
>> Is Florida State being used as a pawn to sell tickets for the College Football Committee?

>> What did the win over Florida say about FSU as a whole 

>> Did off-field distractions finally catchup to Jameis Winston against Florida

>> Is it time for Nebraska and Michigan to have a reality check about their future and hiring a realistic coach
